  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the biodistribution of a new agent 1-L-(2
      deoxy-2,-18fluoroarabinofuranosyl) cytosine non-invasively in healthy humans and to evaluate
      whether it can be used to image cancer, autoimmune disease, and inflammation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
